translations.eng:
Upon pickup, remove [blue]{Cards}[/blue] {Cards:plural:card|cards} from your [gold]Deck[/gold]. After each combat, randomly add [blue]1[/blue] back [gold]Upgraded[/gold].{CardTitles.StringValue:cond:

